<div ng-controller="telAirfareCtrl" layout="column" ng-cloak class="telAirfare">
	<div ng-controller="tuipiaoCtrl" class="tuipiao">
		<md-card class="ml-fontsize-13 ml-color-73">
			<div class="ml-padding-20">
				<div class="ml-fontsize-15 ml-color-21 tuipiao-title blue-line"><span></span>退票详情</div>
				<md-divider></md-divider>
				<md-table-container>
					<table md-table md-row-select multiple ng-model="selected" md-progress="promise" mdSelect="selected">
						<thead md-head md-order="query.order" md-on-reorder="getDesserts">
							<tr md-row>
								<th md-column>退票人姓名(证件号)</th>
								<th md-column md-numeric>类型</th>
								<th md-column md-numeric>票价</th>
								<th md-column md-numeric>基建</th>
								<th md-column md-numeric>燃油</th>
								<th md-column md-numeric>保险金额</th>
								<th md-column md-numeric>EA扣除金额</th>
							</tr>
						</thead>
						<tbody md-body>
							<tr md-row md-select="airfareList" md-select-id="name" md-auto-select ng-repeat="airfareList in airfareLists" ng-dblclick="goAirfareDetail(airfareList)">
								<td md-cell>
									<div>{{airfareList.a}}</div>
									<div>({{airfareList.a}})</div>
								</td>
								<td md-cell>{{airfareList.b}}</td>
								<td md-cell>{{airfareList.c}}</td>
								<td md-cell>{{airfareList.d}}</td>
								<td md-cell>{{airfareList.e}}</td>
								<td md-cell>¥{{airfareList.f}}</td>
								<td md-cell class="ml-color-red">¥{{airfareList.g}}</td>
							</tr>
						</tbody>
					</table>
				</md-table-container>
				<md-divider></md-divider>
				<div class="ml-marginT-20">
					<p>退票原因:航班延误或取消，航班时刻变更，属于［自愿退票］</p>
					<p>退票申请时间:2016-01-23 15:09:22</p>
				</div>
				<p class="ml-marginT-20">
					应扣金额: <span class="ml-color-yellow koukuan">¥344</span>
				</p>
			</div>
			<md-divider></md-divider>
			<div class="ml-padding-20" layout="row" layout-align="center center" layout-wrap>
				<md-button type="submit" ng-disabled="messageUserForm.$invalid" ng-click="addAirfareNext()" class="md-raised md-primary">下一步</md-button>
			</div>
			<div class="tuipiao-bot">
				<div class="tuipiao-bot-in">
					<p>1.退票原因为选择框，供应商计算应该扣除的EA金额也就是订单的结算金额，当退票通过后，EA中可用的金额减掉此部分金额；</p>
					<p>2.操作是由供应商；</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</md-card>
	</div>
</div>